
# Business Data Cleaning, Validation & Excel Reporting

## Problem Summary
Retail order data required cleaning and validation before business analysis.

## Dataset Description
Order-level retail transactions with customer, product, sales, shipping and status information.

## Tools Used
Excel, Python, Pandas, OpenPyXL, Matplotlib.

## Cleaning Steps Performed
Text standardization, date validation, duplicate checks, business rule application, calculated columns.

## Business Rules Applied
Missing region/ship mode replaced with Unknown. Invalid discounts and shipping records flagged.

## Summary of Data Quality Issues Found
Missing values, duplicates, date issues, discount anomalies and status inconsistencies.

## Summary of Final Pivot Reports
Sales by region, category analysis, ship mode counts, segment profit margin, status by region and monthly trends.

## Key Business Insights
Provided through pivot reports.

## Assumptions and Limitations
Automated rule-based cleaning.

## Screenshots Included
Raw data preview, cleaned data preview and two pivot summaries.
